hopobject.body: Your cash is being counted bormioliroccopharmadocs.com In the end, the model would create a single statistic that would account for the individual's breast cancer risk factors and her previous screening decisions and results. Ideally, this statistic would be a starting point for discussion among the radiologist, physician and patient. It would help with mammography decisions of course, but it would also be useful in discussing other breast cancer prevention treatments, such as the drugs tamoxifen or raloxifene.
